description:
What do you believe about God? Have you gotten a distorted picture of God from your religion, your culture, or society? What’s the truth about God? Where can you go to see a picture of God that’s true to character? Walter Veith admits he was deceived about God. He contrasts the distorted features of the character of God that many people have with those portrayed in the Bible story of the prodigal son. How does your picture of God measure up? Is it possible you too have been deceived about God?
